# 样式系统和主题规范

## 组件变体系统

### CVA 变体定义模式

```typescript
import { cva } from "@lynote/utils";

export const buttonVariants = cva(
  // 基础样式
  "inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-colors",
  {
    variants: {
      variant: {
        default: "bg-primary text-primary-foreground hover:bg-primary/90",
        destructive: "bg-destructive text-destructive-foreground hover:bg-destructive/90",
        outline: "border border-input bg-background hover:bg-accent",
        secondary: "bg-secondary text-secondary-foreground hover:bg-secondary/80",
        ghost: "hover:bg-accent hover:text-accent-foreground",
        link: "text-primary underline-offset-4 hover:underline",
      },
      size: {
        default: "h-10 px-4 py-2",
        sm: "h-9 rounded-md px-3",
        lg: "h-11 rounded-md px-8",
        icon: "h-10 w-10",
      },
    },
    defaultVariants: {
      variant: "default",
      size: "default",
    },
  }
);
```

### 变体类型导出

```typescript
export type VariantProps<T extends (...args: any) => any> = Parameters<T>[0];
```

## 样式工具函数

### 类名合并工具 ([packages/core/lib/src/utils.ts](mdc:packages/core/lib/src/utils.ts))

```typescript
import { clsx, type ClassValue } from "clsx";
import { twMerge } from "tailwind-merge";

export function cn(...inputs: ClassValue[]) {
  return twMerge(clsx(inputs));
}
```

### 使用模式

```typescript
import { cn } from "@lynote/utils";
import { buttonVariants } from "./variant";

className={cn(
  buttonVariants({
    variant,
    size,
    color,
    disabled,
  }),
  className
)}
```

## 组件样式集成

### 数据属性样式

使用 `data-*` 属性进行状态相关的样式控制：

```typescript
<div
  data-slot="input"
  data-focus={isFocus}
  data-disabled={disabled}
  className={cn(inputVariants({ size, variant }))}
>
```

### 条件样式

```typescript
className={cn(
  buttonVariants({
    variant,
    size,
    iconModel: !!(icon && !children),
    loading: !!loadingStatus,
    disabled,
  }),
  className
)}
```

## 动画样式集成

### Motion 组件样式

```typescript
import { motion } from "motion/react";

<motion.span
  className={buttonIconVariants()}
  initial={{ opacity: 0, scale: 0.8 }}
  animate={{ opacity: 1, scale: 1 }}
  exit={{ opacity: 0, scale: 0.8 }}
>
  {icon}
</motion.span>
```

## 响应式设计

### Tailwind 响应式前缀

- 使用 Tailwind 的响应式前缀：`sm:`, `md:`, `lg:`, `xl:`
- 移动优先的设计原则

```typescript
const responsiveVariants = cva(
  "text-sm md:text-base lg:text-lg",
  {
    variants: {
      size: {
        sm: "h-8 px-2 sm:h-9 sm:px-3",
        md: "h-10 px-4 sm:h-11 sm:px-6",
        lg: "h-12 px-6 sm:h-14 sm:px-8",
      },
    },
  }
);
```

## 主题定制

### CSS 变量集成

在主题包中定义 CSS 变量：

```css
/* packages/components/src/style/index.css */
:root {
  --background: 0 0% 100%;
  --foreground: 222.2 84% 4.9%;
  --primary: 222.2 47.4% 11.2%;
  --primary-foreground: 210 40% 98%;
  /* ... 其他颜色变量 */
}
```

### 暗色主题支持

```css
.dark {
  --background: 222.2 84% 4.9%;
  --foreground: 210 40% 98%;
  /* ... 暗色主题变量 */
}
```
